# StyleMail

An AI-powered email style replication tool. Upload emails written 
by a specific person and the app learns exactly how they write — 
tone, vocabulary, sentence structure, punctuation habits, phrases. 
Then rewrite or convert any message into that person's exact style.

## What It Does

- Create contact profiles, each with their own writing style
- Upload sample emails per contact to train the style profile
- Compose mode — type what you want to say, get it rewritten in their style
- Convert mode — paste any email, convert it to their style
- Editable output before copying

## Tech Stack

- React + Vite
- OpenAI API (GPT-4o)
- localStorage — no backend, no database
- Deployed on Vercel

## How to Run Locally

npm install
npm run dev

Open http://localhost:5173

## How It Works

Uploaded emails are analyzed by GPT-4o to extract a detailed 
style profile — greetings, sign-offs, sentence length, vocabulary, 
verbatim phrases, punctuation habits, and more. Every generation 
injects the full style profile plus real example emails directly 
into the prompt, keeping output anchored to the real person's voice.